sentences: Lee Yoo-young (Korean:이유영 ; born January 23, 1995), better known mononymously as Yooyoung, Later, the stage name was changed to Lee Hwa-kyum  (Korean:이화겸),  is a South Korean singer and actress.
She made her debut as member of South Korean girl group Hello Venus on May 9, 2012.
In June 2021, Lee signed a contract with Prain TPC.
